      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine. This unit delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies and is mated to a precise 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Performance is optimized via a factory limited-slip differential and Double VANOS variable valve timing. Crucially, this example has undergone preventative subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive VANOS overhaul to ensure structural and mechanical longevity. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and a suspension geometry tuned for neutral handling. While the exterior shows honest patina consistent with a well-loved enthusiast vehicle, the drivetrain is robust and the engine pulls cleanly to its 8,000 RPM redline.",
